INSTALLATION INSTRUCTIONS:

1. MAKE DIRECTORY C:\OPALJR
2. MAKE DIRECTORY C:\OPALJR\DEMO
3. MAKE DIRECTORY C:\OPALJR\EXAMPLES
4. COPY ALL 3BITCOM.*, DECODE3.*, SODAVEND.*, STATE_1.*, AND SYNC_BSM.*
   FILES INTO C:\OPALJR\DEMO.
5. COPY ALL *.EQN FILES, AND EXAMPLES.TXT INTO C:\OPALJR\EXAMPLES.

FOR WINDOWS OPERATION:
1. START WINDOWS.
2. RUN C:\OPALJR\OPALWJR.EXE
AN OPALJR ICON IS NOW AVAILABLE FOR EXECUTION.

FOR DOS OPERATION:
1. EXECUTE C:\OPALJR\OPALJR.EXE
